Two L-159 training aircraft first in foreign hands - in Spain
Two L-159 light combat aircraft out of five that the Czech Ministry of Defence has replaced with the Casa C-295M transport aircraft flew to the Spanish city of Seville on Tuesday, where the Spanish aircraft manufacturer Casa - EADS is based.
