'Mr Espino has the right to appeal to the Comisión de Orden del Consejo Nacional in his case, so that a decision can be taken by a competent authority,' he added.
On the other hand, he said, it was not the time to think about 2012 and that an alliance with the presidential candidates had never been at the negotiating table.
