The UN yesterday proposed in Cancun a plan to renew the lighting of homes, commerce and industry in 100 countries with a view to achieving a reduction in greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions equivalent to almost one third of the additional reductions needed to stabilise the Earth's climate by 2020.
